reviews.text: Delicious Japanese skewers with delightful staff. Cosy and relaxed environment. Quite good with our child too. Don’t miss out on the Japanese grilled yams (our personal favourite), incredibly delicious udon and the crispy rice. Of course the skewers are fantastic too.
Super delicious! I will definitely come back again!

Very friendly and helpful staff, excellent food, and amazing ambience(the background music was gorgeous). We sat at the window and the view was beautiful in the evening. Definitely the perfect restaurant for a special date.
Excellent view. Nice place to enjoy dinner.

result.name: Sai Wan Ho Ferry Pier

reviews.text: The best place to run (jogging). 2 km piers. Pleasant view. Very popular all day long.
Took the ferry back and forth from Kwun Tong. Great little journey, only takes about 10 minutes each way and is an enjoyable view of the bay.
The place is old but the ride is quite enjoyable. Fastest way to get to Kwun Tong.

A good pier to Kwun Tong commerical region. Half hour for a ride, it's convenient. On the course of boat trip, u would enjoy a very spectacular Victoria Harbour view. U just cost HK$9 to reward wonderful journey.

Beware of the company named Coral Sea Ferry. Their staff will try to mislead you to take their ferry to San Ka Tsuen and change to another ferry to Tung Lung Chau (and they will tell people to go to Sai Wan Ho with their ferry if they are already in San Ka Tsuen). The fact is you can take direct ferry to Tung Lung Chau from Sai Wan Ho and it is the quickest path. Just never trust Coral Sea Ferry!

reviews.text:
乘船到觀塘或三家村都很舒服
船價也比乘地鐵便宜

過海到觀塘工商業區，如近西灣河碼頭的話，撘船肯定比地鐵快，因為唔洗行上行落。

船程全程僅>15分鐘。
仿古的碼頭和小渡船、在大海中另有一種風趣。
乘客少!但等候地方整潔
The best place to run (jogging). 2 km piers. Pleasant view. Very popular all day long.

reviews.text:
缺:（無客滿情況）
上菜速度超慢  
等咗1個鐘先有一條香菇，2個鐘先食到兩串肉
帶小朋友不建議去 

優:
服務態度唔錯
啲嘢幾好食
要慢活才能感受上菜速度。 價錢偏高。
對住個海, 景色美麗. 野食 OK
CP值低，水平一般，一次試下夠了。

Delicious Japanese skewers with delightful staff. Cosy and relaxed environment. Quite good with our child too. Don’t miss out on the Japanese grilled yams (our personal favourite), incredibly delicious udon and the crispy rice. Of course the skewers are fantastic too.
